long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Welcome to journey of Urdu! An opportunity for all Urdu lovers. If you want to join us and want to published your urdu poems, lyrics, short stories, articles and news etc.

PICS SWEDEN (Pakistan Information & Cultural Society Sweden) is a non-profit effort in Sweden to keep the Pakistani culture alive. PICS is an initiative of Pakistani expatriate for the purpose of advancement of social and cultural activities of the Pakistani community in Sweden.

Our basic aims are to promote Pakistani culture and portray positive image of Pakistan abroad, promote, develop and propagate Urdu language, provide information about Pakistan and bring Pakistanis from various background together.

Throughout the year, we will host a variety of vibrant events that are not to be missed, including talks, buffet dinners, mushairas, cultural events and support all non-political Pakistani events. So, join today to experience Pakistani spirit and culture!
